metadata.name: Sisakht city at night
metadata.description: I took this photo of  Sisakht city, which is located at two thousand five hundred meters altitude above sea level, on a cold winter night on the top of the opposite mountain. This city is located at the foot of Dena Mountain, the highest mountain in the Zagros Mountains and is the seventh highest city in Iran and is considered a tourist area.Also, due to the similarity of the climate and the similarity of the mountains, the city of Sisakht is known as Switzerland of Iran.
